{"tid":660814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"後費Sir年代最佳 摩佬：我們第2出色","createTime":"2018-05-11T04:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T11:15:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b810439b213cbbb71fec66cb96b27cdb7b2a59c4","tid":660814,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:21:14.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=zWmZ7NaQiltFwnZhPmYJRP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d5a51d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】雖然和波失分，不過曼聯領隊摩連奴沒批評球員之意，又謂目標以逾80分收咧，並預告下仗將以卡域克正選出任隊長，而羅美路把關。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴在球隊與韋斯咸言和0:0後說：「我們是在英超，一個有6支出色球隊嘗試爭標的夢幻般賽事成為次佳球隊。我們得到第2名，我不是完全開心，這不是我本色，但打從我們感覺到不能以冠軍完成的一刻，就把目標訂為第2，而今天是達到了。」<br />\n<br />\n「現在我們的目標是以超過80分完成。」曼聯目前得78分，摩連奴已預告下場，即煞科戰主場對屈福特的部署：「卡域克在奧脫福以隊長身份完成其生涯最後一仗是正常的。迪基亞將會休戰，予羅美路機會出賽，我可作出變動。」<br />\n<br />\n亞軍是曼聯自費格遜榮休，即2012/13年球季奪冠以後的最佳聯賽排位，顯然，摩連奴已放眼5月19日對車路士的足總盃決賽，那是曼聯本季最後的爭標希望。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯近季排名<br />\n球季\t排名<br />\n2017/18\t2<br />\n2016/17\t6<br />\n2015/16\t5<br />\n2014/15\t4<br />\n2013/14\t7<br />\n2012/13\t1"},{"pid":"3cece8f043c6d628c37885633eef1bb096548cda","tid":660814,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/a023f9bb8e71beaec72b507d9b6c6538/tumblr_p8jd12ffCO1vvwgg7o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fa023f9bb8e71beaec72b507d9b6c6538%2Ftumblr_p8jd12ffCO1vvwgg7o1_500.gif&h=e5e797b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/ca82a1b8528bb42235aec99d7b9c6874/tumblr_p8jd12ffCO1vvwgg7o2_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fca82a1b8528bb42235aec99d7b9c6874%2Ftumblr_p8jd12ffCO1vvwgg7o2_500.gif&h=1b02ff22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4b33166e80596122a51eb5d1c233c9471dd1d7f","tid":660814,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20